53:11.440 --> 53:13.180
Dasar pria nakal!

53:21.930 --> 53:23.610
Ini, aku Mr. Ganteng. Memanggil

53:23.610 --> 53:26.340
Roger, komando…

53:26.340 --> 53:28.750
